{"tid":1277362,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"真的要退出？ 英特爾拍賣5G專利","createTime":"2019-07-02T07:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T07:24:01.000Z","uid":73857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b4dbb2e45f7778df1e6df93a7a0710c2c4d71d","tid":1277362,"uid":73857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"〔編譯盧永山／綜合報導〕根據美國IAM報導，英特爾已將失敗的5G數據機晶片事業約8500項專利進行拍賣，希望在8月初獲得報價。<br />\n英特爾要拍賣的專利包括約6000項與3G、4G和5G行動數據機標準有關的專利，1700多項無線執行技術專利，以及500多項在半導體和電子產業有廣泛應用的專利。這項拍賣將交由 Sullivan &amp; Cromwell律師事務所<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2839683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2839683&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=14b60e31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2839683&h=2dbe3991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2839683</a>"}]}